	This large Incense Tower Burner is beautifully carved allows your favourite incense to fragrance the room without being tainted by external factors. Simply light the tip of your incense stick, blow the flame out and place in the specially designed carved features, sit back and enjoy indulgent relaxation with beautiful aroma. Due to the size of the wooden tower you have the option of burning four incense sticks and a cone at the same time so you can combine your favourite fragrances to create your own unique aroma.</p>
